<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Father accidentally runs over 22-month-old girl  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   FAYETTE, N.Y. (AP) - A 22-month-old girl died Friday when she
ran into the path of her father's truck, police said.
</P>
<P>
   Jalisa R. Martin died of head injuries after the 1 p.m. accident
in the driveway of her house.
</P>
<P>
   Police said Ernest M. Martin, 24, was turning his truck around
in the driveway when Jalisa ran out of the yard and was knocked
down by the truck. She was run over by the rear dual wheels.
</P>
<P>
   Police have ruled the death an accident.
</P>
<P>
   Fayette is 37 miles southwest of Syracuse.
</P>
</TEXT>
